.item 'System Problems' 'Added 04/22/88 by AHJ'
System Problems

If you experience system problems during regular business hours, contact
Consulting, 723-2046 for help.

If there is a problem during evening hours, call the Information Desk at
723-4392.

If you experience a serious systems problem during non-business hours, call
Operations at 723-0667 to report the problem.  Please supply as much
information as you can, including your name, Forsythe account, and telephone
number so a Data Center programmer can contact you if necessary.  Operations
will then contact the appropriate people depending on the problem.
